posts.post_title: Looking to Trade T206 PSA 1 Joe Doyle Hands Above Head for Similar SGC version
posts.post_content:
Looking to consolidate my monster set into all SGC graded cards. Up for trade is a nice looking for the grade PSA 1 (PR-FR) Joe Doyle N.Y. Hands Above Head SC 350 Factory 25 version.

Looking to trade for a similarly graded SGC version of this card. I can kick in some $$ if there's a difference in grade. Please shoot me a PM if you have a card that you'd be interested in trading.

Best,

Steve
